# Merinda - News/Blog Magazine Website

## Project Overview

This is a Next.js 15 news/blog magazine website built with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and featuring a modern, responsive design with dark mode support. The project follows Turkish content patterns and uses a component-based architecture.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript 5
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.4.0
- **UI Components**: Radix UI primitives (@radix-ui/react-tabs, @radix-ui/react-slot)
- **Carousels**: Swiper.js 11.2.6
- **Animations**: Framer Motion 12.23.24, GSAP 3.13.0
- **Forms**: React Hook Form 7.65.0 with Zod validation
- **Utilities**: clsx, tailwind-merge, class-variance-authority
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Images**: Next.js Image component with optimization

